"race_medal":0,"score":"1562144802","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"很赞同老师说的：我们要做的是在保证企业“命脉”或核心价值稳定的前提下提升业绩 。<br><br>个人认为做任何事情制定任何方案，都是在保底的情况下不断优化升级，寻求更好。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":103676,"user_name":"Jxin","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1251111,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4C03928388C413","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/17/27/ec30d30a.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1560487146,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1560487146","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"小小开发前来报道。不懂增长，但对所诉也有所理解。没有对错，只有效益。就像限制犯罪不是因为犯罪错误，而是为了降低防卫被犯罪的资源开销，进而提高人们获取资源的积极性。而提高效益就要认清当前饥饿点，然后运用边际效益的思想用更少的资源获得更多的价值。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":100129,"user_name":"bug管理员","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1429196,"ip_address":"","ucode":"7C616B63FEC9C0","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/ce/cc/0ac98381.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1559453821,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1559453821","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"1688电商  现在应该属于成熟期，主要关注客单价、成本率等指标","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":90400,"user_name":"潘浩腾 Peter H. Pan","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1058736,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E5F57A57ED2FB5","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/27/b0/f9775033.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1556509865,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1556509865","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"找准目标后，后续做的事才有意义，否则就是在瞎忙活。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88887,"user_name":"逗逼师父","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1017863,"ip_address":"","ucode":"ECC2D82F83CBE6","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/88/07/7804f4cc.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1556021238,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1556021238","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"我目前负责的产品是房产中介网站，北极星指标是在降低或不增加推广费用的情况下，增加电话点击的数量。<br><br>推广费用是实实在在在花费的成本，并且资金有限。<br>而电话点击数虽然不是一个理想的衡量转化的指标，但是是最接近转化环节的可量化指标。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88656,"user_name":"洛奇","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1498111,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3C105A7CE61C4E","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/db/ff/6ae3913c.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555980046,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555980046","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"产品底线具体指的是什么？刘老师可以举例说明下吗？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88364,"user_name":"Hunter Liu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1474463,"ip_address":"","ucode":"BD1FD203A295DC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/7f/9f/ca7b20cd.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555912016,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555912016","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"在老师讲解的时候我就在想我的北极星指标是什么，后来我想到了，就是现有产品要加入新功能，并且可以在低性能的硬件平台上很好的运行。可是很多功能工程师们已经评估了性能低是无法运行的，即使可以，也要非常长的周期，这个矛盾点怎么破？","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":88186,"user_name":"易林林","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1049836,"ip_address":"","ucode":"27F84A3FCBBCAD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/04/ec/0539c89d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1555891574,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1555891574","product_id":100025001,"comment_content":"根据我的理解，北极星指标分为短期指标和长期指标。短期指标的根本目的是爆炸式的红利，而长期指标的核心目的是持续性的利益，这就需要去平衡资本和增长的预期是否符合多方面的要求。","like_count":0}]}